    <h2>🏪 Our Story</h2>
    <p>ShopIndia was founded with one simple mission — to make quality products accessible to every Indian at honest prices. We partner with verified suppliers across India and globally to bring you the best deals on fashion, electronics, beauty, home decor and more.</p>
    <h2>🎯 Our Mission</h2>
    <p>To be India's most trusted dropshipping marketplace — connecting millions of customers with the best products at the best prices, with zero compromise on quality or service.</p>
    <h2>📦 How It Works</h2>
    <p>We follow a 100% dropshipping model — we don't hold inventory. When you place an order, we source it fresh from our verified supplier network and ship it directly to your doorstep. This means fresher stock, better prices, and a wider selection for you.</p>
    <h2>💚 Our Promise</h2>
    <p>✅ Genuine products only<br>✅ Transparent pricing — no hidden fees<br>✅ 7-day return guarantee<br>✅ Fast customer support via WhatsApp<br>✅ Secure UPI & COD payments</p>
    <h2>📞 Contact Us</h2>
    <p>WhatsApp: <strong>+91 78660 48085</strong><br>UPI: <strong>tanvir786@ptaxis</strong></p>
  </div>
</div>

