<!-- ===================== SHIPPING POLICY PAGE ===================== -->
<div class="page" id="page-shipping-policy">
  <div class="page-header">
    <button class="back-btn" onclick="goBack()">←</button>
    <span class="page-title">Shipping Policy</span>
  </div>
  <div class="policy-body">
    <h2>🚚 Free Shipping</h2>
    <p>Free standard shipping on all orders above ₹499. Orders below ₹499 attract a flat ₹49 delivery charge.</p>
    <h2>⏱️ Delivery Timeframes</h2>
    <p><strong>Standard Delivery:</strong> 4–6 business days<br><strong>Express Delivery:</strong> 1–2 business days (+₹99)</p>
    <p>Delivery times may vary for remote areas (Northeast India, Jammu & Kashmir, Ladakh, Andaman & Nicobar). Allow 7–10 days for such locations.</p>
    <h2>📍 Pincode Serviceability</h2>
    <p>We deliver to 20,000+ pincodes across India. Enter your pincode on the product page to check delivery availability. We're continuously expanding our reach.</p>
    <h2>📦 Order Processing</h2>
    <p>Orders are processed within 1–2 business days after payment confirmation. You will receive a WhatsApp/SMS notification when your order is dispatched with tracking details.</p>
    <h2>🏷️ Shipping Partners</h2>
    <p>We ship via trusted courier partners including Delhivery, BlueDart, Ekart, Xpressbees, and India Post depending on your location.</p>
    <h2>⚠️ Important Notes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Business days exclude Sundays and public holidays</li>
      <li>During sale seasons, delivery may take 1–2 extra days</li>
      <li>COD orders may incur an additional ₹30–50 handling fee</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===================== RETURN POLICY PAGE ===================== -->
<div class="page" id="page-return-policy">
  <div class="page-header">
    <button class="back-btn" onclick="goBack()">←</button>
    <span class="page-title">Return & Refund Policy</span>
  </div>
  <div class="policy-body">
    <h2>↩️ 7-Day Return Policy</h2>
    <p>We offer hassle-free returns within 7 days of delivery for eligible items. To initiate a return, contact us on WhatsApp with your Order ID and reason.</p>
    <h2>✅ Eligible for Return</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Damaged or defective product</li>
      <li>Wrong item delivered</li>
      <li>Product significantly different from listing</li>
      <li>Missing parts or accessories</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>❌ Not Eligible for Return</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Used, washed, or altered products</li>
      <li>Items without original packaging (if applicable)</li>
      <li>Perishable goods (food, beauty products opened)</li>
      <li>Intimate wear, lingerie (hygiene reasons)</li>
      <li>Products with tampered serial/IMEI numbers</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>💰 Refund Process</h2>
    <p><strong>UPI/Online Payments:</strong> Refunded to original payment method within 5–7 business days after return pickup.<br><strong>COD Orders:</strong> Refunded via UPI/bank transfer. Share your UPI ID when raising return request.</p>
    <h2>📞 How to Return</h2>
    <p>1. WhatsApp us at +91 78660 48085 within 7 days of delivery<br>2. Share Order ID + photos of the issue<br>3. Our team will arrange a free pickup<br>4. Refund processed after inspection</p>
  </div>
</div>

